author: arfrever
msg: * autogen.py: Use ctypesgen.py instead of wrap.py.

author: julianfoad
msg: In the test suite's checking of multi-line property values, fix a line-ending
quirk and make the parsing a bit more robust and simpler.
dont_add_mergeinfo_from_own_history): Remove the spurious newline from
the end of the expected mergeinfo value.
(get_props): Don't add an extra newline to a multi-line property value.
Be more careful in matching a property name line. When stripping the
line-ending characters, avoid accidentally stripping other white space
from the beginning or end of a line.

author: julianfoad
msg: In the test suite, factor out some checking of properties, in order to avoid
every test parsing the output of "svn proplist" itself.
(check_proplist): Use svntest.tree.get_props() instead of parsing the
output of "svn proplist" here. Remove a redundant argument.
